Business Transformation Leader in the newly created Consumer Health Joint Venture management team, focused on defining Business Transformation strategy and future organization design while building and nurturing high performing team and supporting exploration of new value spaces and development of meaningful propositions to deliver quadruple aim. 

Key responsibilities and achievements:

- Structured and led 2 strategic Cluster Marketing initiatives (Commercial Unlocks & Next Gen.Customer Experience) to bring voice and needs of Customer closer to the business, and deliver growth on top of the annual business targets utilizing Agile WoW and OKR framework;

- Supported cross-cluster Venture teams in Consumer Health JV in shaping path forward, building agile and program management capabilities, and setting up efficient cross-functional process framework to speed up execution in the Venture business;

- Provided coaching to Management Team and their teams in the practical application of the LEAN tools, Agile and Change Management to drive operational excellence and create a transformational vision for meaningful, long-term business success.

- Prepared and facilitated meetings a for informed decision making and leadership support with Busines Leaders and Executives

Being part of the Beauty business management team and PH Cluster playing a key role in both perform and transform initiatives to enable business results and sustainable growth, while driving Lean, Agile, Customer focus and quality mindset at Philips.

Key responsibilities and achievements:

- Led a cross-functional team of senior MT members to drive business performance in 2020, resulting in CSG% improvement (-25.5% -> -0.3%) and adj. Ebita (-2.2% -> 14.1%)

- Established and managed E2E Productivity Program for a Personal Health Cluster (€3.4Bln) resulting in €37M savings in the first 7 months;

- Provided coaching to Management Team in the practical application of the LEAN tools, Agile and Change Management to drive operational excellence and create a transformational vision for meaningful, long-term business success.

- Facilitated 300+ meetings and working sessions for informed decision making and leadership support with senior directors and executives;

Supplier (construction wood, flooring, facade boards, wooden doors) for global DIY stores in Poland, France and Ukraine: Castorama, Brico Depot, Praktiker & OBI. Key areas of responsibility:
• Managing B2B and B2C customer relationships;
• Negotiating purchase conditions with suppliers and buyers;
• Coordinating workflow between order management, manufacturing and distribution centers;
• Overseeing S&OP and S&OE processes;
• Identifying and addressing problems and opportunities for the company across the value chain;

